dct_description_sm: New Jersey. Department of Conservation and Development. Division of Geology and Waters. Atlas Sheet 29 (1924) New Jersey Geological Survey. Relief shown by 10 ft. contour interval and spot heights. Depth of water shown by fathom in feet at low tide. Title is not given. Region covered: Monmouth Shore. Original survey , 1884; principal features revised. 1909, 1914, 1923. Original survey and revisions to 1914 made under direction of C. C. Vermeule, Topographer. Revision of 1923 by L. P. Plummer, Topographic Engineer.
dct_publisher_sm: Trenton, N.J. : New Jersey Geological Survey, 1924.
